'''''Casus Belli'' 99''' was a French roleplaying magazine from November of [[1996]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including two adventures for the [[West End Games]] ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game|D6]] system. The articles were called "[[Galactic Born Killer!]]" written by [[Patrick Bousquet]] and "[[La somme de toutes les peurs]]" (in English "The Sum of All Their Fears") written by [[Christophe Debien]].

